c: 8
v: 12
t: "Nabiyow ku Rabbi Malaykal wacyi oobise waqdi cusey, diggah anu catooy Qokoluh siinî luk aniyok, toysa yeemeneh yan marih niya diggi haysa anu koroositeh yan marih lubbittet conxo Qideyyok, toysa moominiiney isin moyyaayii keenik atukaay feeraarik exaaxi inkih keenik atuka ibittee kee gaboobik iyyaanamah"